      "span_text": "As we continue to debate how we may overcome these issues, it is important to remember that previous concerns about greater transparency in medical practice, such as improving patient access to their doctors' notes, have almost always led to increased patient satisfaction and compliance with their medical care.  Ensuring elevated surgical quality consistently across all providers is complex.",
